  "text": "A variety of auto-antigens have also been suggested in AIP, including antilactoferrin and anticarbonic anhydrase II or -IV [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Antibodies to pancreatic secretory trypsin inhibitor and an amino acid sequence of plasminogenbinding protein (anti-PBP) have also been implicated [CITATION_3] .",
